import './style.css'
import {Form,FormGroup,Label,Input,Button} from 'reactstrap';

const form =()=>{
    return (
        <Form inline>
  <FormGroup>
        <Label for="exampleCity">
          City
        </Label>
        <Input
          id="exampleCity"
          name="city"
        />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="exampleState">
          State
        </Label>
        <Input
          id="exampleState"
          name="state"
        />
      </FormGroup>
  {' '}
  <FormGroup>
    <Label
      for="examplePassword"
      hidden
    >
      Password
    </Label>
    <Input
      id="examplePassword"
      name="password"
      placeholder="Password"
      type="password"
    />
  </FormGroup>
  {' '}
  <Button>
    Submit
  </Button>
</Form>
    )
}
export default form
